snippet: Author Jamaica Kincaid and film critic Armond White are among the winners of the 35th annual American Book Awards, which celebrate multiculturalism and free expression....

headline.print_headline: Jamaica Kincaid Wins American Book Award
headline.main: Jamaica Kincaid Wins American Book Award

lead_paragraph: Author Jamaica Kincaid and film critic Armond White are among the winners of the 35th annual American Book Awards, which celebrate multiculturalism and free expression.
